text: Bundfald is a 1957 Danish crime drama movie directed by Palle Kjærulff-Schmidt and Robert Saaskin. It stars Birgitte Bruun, Ib Mossin, Ghita Nørby, Jø Jeppesen, Jakob Nielsen, Lone Hertz and Preben Kaas. ==Other websites== * Category:1957 crime drama movies Category:Danish crime movies Category:Danish drama movies Category:Movies directed by Palle Kjærulff-Schmidt Category:Movies set in Copenhagen Category:Movies about juvenile delinquency
